  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.8.0-alpha01\" data-text=\"Version 1.8.0-alpha01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.8.0-alpha01</h3>\n<p>February 21, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.annotation:annotation-*:1.8.0-alpha01</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/bff33338af8303e6c2540b14ec3d7960f7f7a15d..e1b82c49c59d8e976ce558aba5586f6c61bc9054/annotation/annotation\">Version 1.8.0-alpha01 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>API Changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">@ReplaceWith</code> annotation to express replacements for deprecated APIs. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I38db39789f657e70e962cae2e3360023db50ecb5\">I38db3</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/322373864\">b/322373864</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>External Contributions</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Thanks Ivan Matkov for moving the <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">@MainThread</code> annotation to the common source set. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/6f228cd685f996a6d6ad7f757ea6b71b5b248f5d\">6f228c</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"version_17_2\" data-text=\"Version 1.7\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.7</h2>",
